        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThinking ahead about recovery. If a subset of policies succeed, and a subset fails. Possibly re-distribution can be done via the SDC GUI. It could be done in any circumstance. Do we think we are able to handle that very likely situation? Any past failed policies may *possibly* work again? As well as any policies that were previously loaded as part of success scenario, would gently error out?",
